1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
I can't believe we actually made it here.

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:06,000
This place is absolutely beautiful!

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,500
But I'm worried about what happens next.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Don't be scared, we'll figure it out together.

5
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,000
That makes me so happy to hear you say that.

6
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:19,500
Wait, did you hear that noise? What was that?

7
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,000
It was nothing, just the wind blowing through the trees.

8
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:26,500
I hate this, I just want to go home already.

9
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Oh wow, look at that sunset! It's incredible!

10
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:33,000
I know, moments like these are what life is about.
